Enhancement: Add per snapshot description

Restic can now store user supplied descriptions for snapshots.
When creating a new snapshot the description can be supplied
using `restic backup --description <description>` or
`restic backup --description-file <filepath>`.

`restic snapshots` shows the snapshots description.

`restic rewrite [--description <description> | --description-file <filepath>] <snapshot id>`
is used to change the description of existing snapshots.

To remove a description use `restic rewrite --remove-description <snapshot id>`.

https://github.com/restic/restic/issues/2376
https://github.com/restic/restic/pull/5375
